ider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fwhere-to-buy-ray-ban-meta-glasses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20Ray-Ban%20glasses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20(which%20doesn't%20require%20the%20glasses)%20is%20to%20be%20a%20stand-alone%20Meta%20AI%20assistant%20that%20you%20may%20have%20already%20encountered%20in%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20search.%20Basically%2C%20it's%20a%20chatbot%20app%20that%20(I%20guess%3F)%20is%20meant%20to%20compete%20with%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20part%20of%20the%20app%20is%20pretty%20familiar.%20Meta%20AI%20can%20answer%20questions%2C%20chat%20with%20you%2C%20and%20make%20funny%20pictures%20for%20you%2C%20like%20this%20one%20I%20had%20made%20of%20a%20dog%20reading%20BI%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20the%20meta%20ai%20app%20asking%20it%20to%20make%20a%20dog%20pic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813bbe8c6ad288d147fbf6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20asked%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20new%20Meta%20AI%20did%20it%2C%20with%20a%20slight%20misspelling.%20Still%2C%20pretty%20good!%3Cp%3EMeta%20AI%20%2F%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20where%20it%20gets%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20public%20feed%20of%20other%20people's%20AI%20chats%20that%20you%20can%20scroll%20through.%20Most%20of%20this%20feed%20is%20people%20making%20silly%20images%20%E2%80%94%20Darth%20Vader%20eating%20ice%20cream%2C%20that%20sort%20of%20thing.%20Some%20of%20these%20came%20from%20suggested%20prompts%20when%20you%20first%20open%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20your%20AI%20chats%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20public%20by%20default%20%E2%80%94%20you%20have%20to%20choose%20to%20share%20them%20individually%20by%20tapping%20a%20share%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20so%2C%20I%20get%20the%20sense%20that%20some%20people%20don't%20really%2