der.com%2Fdc-plane-crash-timeline-atc-american-airlines-helicopter-collision-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%20midair%20collision%20over%20Washington%2C%20DC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20preliminary%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20airport%20tower%20was%20understaffed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20has%20continued%20in%20other%20busy%20airspaces.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Newark%20Liberty%20International%20Airport%20in%20New%20Jersey%20experienced%20a%20breakdown%20in%20airline%20operations%20due%20to%20air%20traffic%20constraints%2C%20including%20too%20few%20controllers%20and%20an%20equipment%20outage%2C%20causing%20delays%20and%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-upgrades-air-safety-dc-crash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFAA%20aims%20to%20upgrade%20antiquated%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20hire%202%2C000%20new%20controllers%20in%202025%2C%20the%20latter%20sped%20up%20by%20reducing%20the%20previous%208-step%20hiring%20process%20to%20five%20and%20boosting%20academy%20trainee%20pay%20by%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-traffic-controllers-workload-stress-alcohol-drugs-faa-close-calls-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAspiring%20controllers%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20need%20a%20college%20degree%20but%20must%20be%20under%20the%20age%20of%2031%20and%20meet%20certain%20education%2C%20physical%2C%20and%20mental%20fitness%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20it%20has%20cut%20five%20months%20off%20the%20hiring%20timeline%20and%20sent%20more%20than%208%2C300%20candidates%20to%20take%20the%20air%20traffic%20skills%20aptitude%20test%20to%20determine%20their%20admission%20to%20the%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLess%20than%2045%20days%20after%20the%20announcement%20closed%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20applicants%20already%20has%20an%20Academy%20start%20d