22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20App%20Store%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20does%3A%20The%20fees%20are%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20revenue%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20fighting%20efforts%20to%20cut%20into%20them%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20ruling%20from%20a%20federal%20judge%20may%20cut%20into%20them.%20If%20it%20holds%20up%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20major%20change%20for%20Apple.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20just%20slapped%20Apple%20around%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.364265%2Fgov.uscourts.cand.364265.1508.0_2.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYvonne%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20said%20Apple%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bwillful%20violation%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%202021%20ruling%20she%20had%20made%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudge-finds-apple-executive-lied-under-oath-refers-criminal-investigation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20she%20would%20refer%20the%20company%20for%20a%20possible%20criminal%20prosecution%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20pretty%20newsworthy.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20rest%20of%20Rogers'%20ruling%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20that%20could%20be%20pretty%20newsworthy%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%3Cem%3Epossible%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20could%20finally%20be%20the%20thing%20that%20fundamentally%20changes%20the%20way%20Apple%20operates%20its%20App%20Store%20%E2%80%94%20an%20increasingly%20key%20source%20of%20the%20company's%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20it%20might%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20ruling%20comes%20out%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-epic-games-legal-case-opening-remarks-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourt%20battle%20between%20Apple%20and%20Epic%20Games%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company%20that%20operates%20Fortnite%2C%20that%20started%20back%20in%20nearly%20five%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nutshell%3A%20Epic%20doesn't%20like%20that%20Apple%20requires%20Fortnite%20players%20and%20anyone%20else%20using%20iOS%20devices%20to%20make%20in-app%20purchases%20via%20Apple's%20homegrown%20App%20Store%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20Apple%20can%20pocket%20up%20to%2030%25%20of%20each%20transaction.%20In%20the%20summer%20of%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Frecode%2F2020%2F8%2F13%2F21366340%2Ffortnite-epic-apple-app-store-ios-antitrust%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpic%20deliberately%20violated%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20led%20to%20Apple%20essentially%20kicking%20Fortnite%20off%20of%20its%20iPhones%20and%20iPads%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20civil%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpic%20appeared%20to%20have%20lost%20its%20fight%20in%202021%2C%20when%20Rogers%20ruled%20against%20it%20on%20almost%20all%20counts.%20But%20Epic%20did%20salvage%20one%20win%3A%20Rogers%20said%20Apple%20had%20to%20let%20developers%20like%20Epic%20tell%20customers%20that%20they%20could%20leave%20the%20app%20and%20head%20to%20another%20website%2C%20where%20they%20could%20make%20transactions%20without%20Apple's%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20ruling%20holds%20that%20Apple%20violated%20both%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20the%20original%20ruling%20and%20says%20Apple%20has%20to%20comply%20with%20it%20immediately.%20Meaning%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20that%20companies%20like%20Epic%20will%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20their%20customers%20using%20iPhones%20that%20they%20can%20get%20a%20better%20deal%20somewhere%20else%2C%20and%20that%20Apple%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20charge%20developers%20an%20onerous%20fee%20if%20that%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Apple%20rep%20says%20it%20will%20comply%20with%20the%20ruling%2C%20but%20will%20also%20appeal%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20on%20the%20one%20hand%3A%20This%20could%20be%20an%20enormous%20issue%20for%20Apple.%20If%20big%20players%20like%20Epic%20routinely%20convince%20customers%20to%20do%20transactions%20with%20them%20outside%20of%20Apple's%20app%2C%20it%20could%20cut%20into%20Apple's%20growing%20%26quot%3Bservices%26quot%3B%20business%20%E2%80%94%20an%20increasingly%20important%20part%20of%20Apple's%20income%20statement%2C%20as%20its%20core%20iPhone%20revenues%20flatten%20out.%20And%20it%20comes%20as%20Apple%20is%20facing%20similar%20battles%20around%20the%20world%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-meta-big-tech-eu-fine-donald-trump-tariffs-negotiation-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20European%20Union%20just%20fined%20Apple%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20of%20the%20way%20it%20operates%20the%20App%20Store%20in%20that%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%3A%20As%20noted%20above%2C%20Apple%20will%20appeal%20Rogers'%20ruling.%20So%20it's%20possible%20that%20the%20buy-outside-the-App-Store%20option%20won't%20be%20an%20option%20in%20the%20US%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20important%3A%20What%20percentage%20of%20Apple%20users%20actually%20want%20to%20leave%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20to%20buy%20stuff%20for%20the%20games%20they're%20playing%3F%20We%20have%20no%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20will%20be%20motivated%20to%20do%20it%2C%20since%20they%20can%20theoretically%20get%20more%20for%20their%20money%20if%20Apple%20isn't%20taking%20a%20cut%20for%20itself.%20Or%20maybe%20most%20of%20them%20won't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20headaches%20of%20jumping%20out%20of%20an%20app%2C%20pulling%20out%20a%20credit%20card%20(or%20asking%20their%20parents%20for%20their%20credit%20card)%2C%20and%20making%20purchases%20on%20a%20different%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20find%20out%20soon.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Ftimsweeneyepic%2Fstatus%2F1917716512347152499%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEpic%20CEO%20Tim%20Sweeney%20says%20he%20will%20bring%20Fortnite%20back%20to%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20next%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20not%20clear%2C%20however%2C%20if%20Apple%20has%20agreed%20to%20that.%20I've%20asked%20both%20companies%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746124499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813ba4dc6ad288d147fbeee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tim%20Cook%20increasingly%20counts%20on%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20fees.%20Will%20a%20US%20court%20ruling%20in%20a%20case%20with%20Epic%20Games%20reshape%20the%20tech%20giant's%20revenue%20model%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store-court-ruling-epic-game-charges-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20are%20using%20IoT%20to%20take%20the%20guesswork%20out%20of%20growing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Build%20IT%20Illustration%20of%20a%20farmer%20looking%20on%20at%20farmland%20shifting%20into%20tech-driven%20directions%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68129477a466d2b74ab4aa18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGlenn%20Harvey%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fbuild-it-connectivity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBuild%20IT%3A%20Connectivity%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20about%20tech%20powering%20better%20business.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStakes%20are%20high%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurveys%20have%20found%20they're%20eager%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bcg.com%2Fpublications%2F2024%2Fwhat-1000-farmers-told-us-about-tech-adoption%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frissman.russell.wisc.edu%2Fpolicy-analysis%2F2024-farmer-survey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecut%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Findustries%2Fagriculture%2Four-insights%2Fglobal-farmer-insights-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresources%20wisely%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTo%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20a%20growing%20population%2C%20we%20need%20to%20make%20things%20more%20efficient%20and%20increase%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20David%20Cappelleri%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Purdue%20University%20and%20a%20site%20director%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiot4ag.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternet%20of%20Things%20for%20Precision%20Agriculture%20research%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20IoT4Ag.%20%26quot%3BOne%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20adding%20new%20technologies%20to%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrecision%20agriculture%20technologies%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20way%20forward%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20interest%20gathering%20around%20Internet%20of%20Things%20technology.%20These%20IoT%20systems%20combine%20different%20pieces%20of%20technology%20to%20collect%2C%20communicate%2C%20and%20apply%20real-time%20data.%20Tools%20include%20devices%20equipped%20with%20sensors%2C%20wireless%20technologies%20like%20cellular%20networks%2C%20and%20data%20processing%20technologies%20such%20as%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20soil%20sensor%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20detect%20the%20conditions%20needed%20for%20better%20crops.%20Bringing%20together%20IoT-collected%20data%20allows%20farmers%20to%20better%20manage%20soil%2C%20fertilizer%2C%20and%20water%2C%20and%20reduce%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECappelleri%20said%20that%20while%20we're%20still%20in%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20IoT-fueled%20precision%20agriculture%2C%20the%20technology%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20difference.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20he%20added%2C%20there%20will%20be%20hurdles%2C%20like%20expanding%20connectivity%20coverage%20and%20simplifying%20the%20use%20of%20this%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20technology%20is%20ripe%20for%20this%20to%20happen%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Cappelleri%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20way%20to%20use%20data%2C%20and%20the%20key%20is%20to%20show%20the%20value%20to%20farmers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b399db8c-f6b8-40cc-8256-f4e7439c71dd%5C%22%3EHarvesting%20data%3A%20IoT%20and%20precision%20agriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagricultural-drones-precision-mapping-spraying%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrecision%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20approach%20to%20farming%20that%20uses%20data%2C%20such%20as%20crop%20health%20measurements%2C%20to%20help%20growers%20make%20more%20targeted%20decisions%20and%20speed%20up%20their%20farming%20practices.%20While%20the%20concept%20has%20existed%20for%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS016816992200059X%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20advancement%20of%20IoT%20allows%20different%20technologies%20to%20work%20together%20to%20build%20a%20better%20farming%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECherie%20Kagan%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20and%20the%20center%20director%20of%20IoT4Ag.%20Launched%20in%202020%2C%20the%20US%20research%20center%2C%20which%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20National%20Science%20Foundation%2C%20brings%20together%20faculty%20from%20different%20universities%2C%20industry%20professionals%2C%20and%20farmers%20to%20support%20the%20development%20of%20precision%20agriculture%20IoT%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKagan%20said%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20there%20have%20been%20major%20advancements%20in%20hardware%20technology%2C%20data%20science%2C%20and%20information%20technology%2C%20all%20of%20which%20support%20IoT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20starting%20the%20center%2C%20we%20realized%20this%20exponential%20growth%20meant%20the%20time%20was%20right%20for%20a%20very%20different%2C%20and%20very%20important%2C%20opportunity%20for%20this%20tech%2C%26quot%3B%20Kagan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229426%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20biodegradable%20sensor%20on%20a%20leaf.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813b5d9a466d2b74ab4c152%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227069%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIoT4Ag%20team%20members%20are%20developing%20a%20biodegradable%20leaf%20sensor.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20IoT4Ag%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECenter%20researchers%20work%20on%20all%20parts%20of%20an%20IoT%20system%2C%20such%20as%20the%20sensors%20that%20collect%20data%2C%20the%20communication%20network%20that%20helps%20send%20the%20data%2C%20and%20the%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-cloud-computing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20or%20edge%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20that%20stores%2C%20processes%2C%20and%20analyzes%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20as%20part%20of%20IoT4AG%2C%20Kagan%20is%20developing%20biodegradable%20sensors%20for%20soil%20and%20leaves.%20Leaf%20sensors%20can%20measure%20moisture%20and%20temperature%20levels%2C%20and%20soil%20sensors%20can%20detect%20essential%20nutrients%20like%20nitrate%2C%20offering%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20monitor%20crop%20health%20and%20spot%20issues%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Cappelleri%20and%20his%20team%20are%20working%20on%20ground%20and%20aerial%20robots%20that%20use%20sensors%20to%20measure%20crop%20health%20and%20work%20together%20with%20in-field%20IoT%20sensors%2C%20like%20the%20sort%20Kagan%20is%20developing.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20sensor%20is%20buried%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20robot%20can%20drive%20over%20it%2C%20read%20the%20data%2C%20and%20wirelessly%20send%20that%20information%20to%20a%20cloud%20platform%20through%20a%20communication%20system%2C%20such%20as%20a%205G%20cellular%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECappelleri%20told%20BI%20that%20consistent%20measurements%2C%20enabled%20by%20this%20type%20of%20tech%2C%20could%20tell%20farmers%20what%20is%20and%20isn't%20working.%20This%20could%20help%20farmers%20make%20decisions%20%26quot%3Bin%20season%2C%20week%20by%20week%2C%20rather%20than%20waiting%20until%20next%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8e111c9-6d5a-431c-b8f2-7328361a48f8%5C%22%3EGrowing%20smarter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Caro%20C%C3%B3rdova%20talks%20to%20farmers%20in%20Nebraska%20about%20what's%20most%20important%20to%20them%2C%20they're%20quick%20to%20mention%20saving%20time%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC%C3%B3rdova%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nebraska-Lincoln%2C%20works%20closely%20with%20these%20farmers%20to%20improve%20soil%20health%2C%20which%20is%20vital%20to%20food%20production.%20She's%20working%20with%20soil%20sensors%20to%20see%20how%20the%20tech%20compares%20with%20traditional%20ways%20of%20analyzing%20soil%20in%20a%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20sensors%20in%20place%20that%20monitor%20properties%20like%20moisture%2C%20nutrients%2C%20and%20pH%20helps%20us%20monitor%20the%20soil%20in%20real%20time%20and%20manage%20resources%20more%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20C%C3%B3rdova%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%2C%20for%20example%2C%20minimize%20the%20application%20of%20fertilizers%20or%20reduce%20water%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20product%20on%20the%20market%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fteralytic.com%2Fsoil-probe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%20by%20Teralytic%2C%20an%20agriculture%20technology%20company.%20It%20has%2026%20sensors%20and%20can%20measure%20various%20elements%2C%20including%20soil%20moisture%2C%20salinity%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20nutrients%2C%20at%20three%20different%20soil%20depths.%20If%20more%20nutrients%20are%20needed%20in%20the%20soil%2C%20fertilizers%20can%20supplement%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Teralytic%20soil%20probe%20in%20the%20dirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813b8bcc6ad288d147fbe9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Teralytic%20soil%20probe%20checks%20and%20reports%20on%20factors%20like%20soil%20moisture%2C%20salinity%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20essential%20nutrients.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Teralytic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sensor-collected%20data%20is%20wirelessly%20transmitted%20via%20LoRaWAN%2C%20tech%20that%20sends%20information%20through%20low-power%2C%20long-range%20radio%20waves.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20data%20makes%20its%20way%20to%20Teralytic's%20cloud%20platform%2C%20where%20the%20company%20runs%20analytics.%20The%20findings%20are%20displayed%20for%20the%20user%20on%20an%20online%20dashboard%20with%20real-time%20charts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGrowers%20might%20have%20a%20field%20with%20a%20trouble%20spot%2C%20but%20they've%20lacked%20the%20understanding%20of%20what's%20exactly%20wrong%20because%20normally%20you%20would%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20physically%20collect%20soil%20samples%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Mansergh%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20research%20and%20development%20at%20Teralytic%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20IoT%20really%20helps%2C%20because%20instead%20of%20waiting%20for%20the%20results%20of%20that%20long%20process%2C%20they%20can%20now%20have%20a%20really%20clear%20picture%20of%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb670d70-9049-4dca-9434-8da5b6c24509%5C%22%3EGetting%20more%20farmers%20connected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELuke%20James%2C%20a%20dealer-success%20manager%20at%20Ag%20Leader%2C%20a%20precision%20agriculture%20company%2C%20has%20seen%20the%20technology%20evolve%20in%20his%20nearly%20two%20decades%20at%20the%20firm.%20He%20said%20the%20past%20five%20years%20had%20been%20especially%20transformative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20exploded%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20consumer%20technology%20making%20its%20way%20into%20agriculture.%20Companies%20are%20now%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20leverage%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20technology%20and%20helping%20growers%20benefit%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20said%20farmers%20appreciate%20the%20IoT%20process%20because%20of%20the%20insights%20and%20ease%20of%20use.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20what's%20happening%20in%20real%20time%20across%20the%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20farmer%20using%20agriculture%20technology%20from%20Ag%20Leader.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6813b8c93fe8d3928364a989%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAg%20Leader%20develops%20different%20agtech%20products%2C%20like%20the%20InCommand%20Go%2016%2C%20a%20high-resolution%20touchscreen%20display%20that%20shows%20real-time%20farm%20data.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Ag%20Leader%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20that%20some%20of%20his%20customers%20are%20in%20rural%20areas%20where%20cell%20coverage%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5g-transforms-businesses-better-security-remote-capabilities-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E5G%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20types%20of%20connectivity%20are%20difficult%20to%20access%2C%20limiting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fagtech-valuations-were-crushed-in-2023-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagtech%3C%2Fa%3E%20available%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20pushing%20hard%20for%20our%20growers%20to%20get%20connected%20because%20it%20does%20open%20up%20another%20swath%20of%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202024%20paper%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20Frontiers%20in%20Sustainable%20Food%20Systems%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Esuggested%20connectivity%20issues%20were%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Fjournals%2Fsustainable-food-systems%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffsufs.2024.1456991%2Ffull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprimary%3C%2Fa%3E%20factors%20limiting%20the%20adoption%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffermata-artificial-intelligence-technology-for-agriculture-plant-crop-health-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20agriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20includes%20precision%20farming.%20A%202023%20US%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20study%20found%20that%2027%25%20of%20US%20farms%20or%20ranches%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gao.gov%2Fproducts%2Fgao-24-105962%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20precision%20agriculture%20practices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC%C3%B3rdova%20said%20that%20while%20IoT%20data%20could%20be%20sent%20in%20several%20ways%2C%20how%20much%20data%20can%20be%20moved%20depends%20on%20the%20network.%20If%205G%20isn't%20available%2C%20farmers%20can%20try%20to%20use%20other%20communication%20networks%2C%20like%20WiFi%20and%20satellite%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EC%C3%B3rdova%20said%20high%20costs%20and%20a%20technology%20learning%20curve%20were%20other%20barriers%20to%20IoT%20adoption.%20She%20added%20that%20there's%20also%20a%20need%20for%20more%20data%20analytics%20services%20to%20provide%20farmers%20with%20clear%20and%20useful%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20sensors%20are%20collecting%20data%20in%20real%20time%2C%20sometimes%20every%20five%20seconds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20incredible%20amount%20of%20data%2C%20but%20to%20be%20useful%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20feedback%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKagan%20said%20that%20overcoming%20these%20obstacles%20would%20require%20more%20collaboration%20between%20researchers%2C%20policymakers%2C%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20and%20farmers.%20Precision%20agriculture%20powered%20by%20IoT%20is%20already%20helping%20farmers%20operate%2C%20she%20said%2C%20but%20further%20partnerships%20and%20the%20right%20investments%20could%20facilitate%20a%20more%20resilient%20food%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20challenge%20is%20bringing%20together%20all%20these%20technologies%20in%20a%20way%20that%20provides%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20Kagan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20very%20important%20to%20have%20these%20different%20stakeholders%20work%20together.%20We%20need%20each%20other's%20input%20to%20really%20make%20it%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiot-technology-precision-agriculture-transforming-farming-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746124230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681294a43fe8d39283649186%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi