onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F423598%2Fpalaash-near-tipai-tipeshwar-wildlife-sanctuary-nagpur-maharashtra-farm-to-table-dining%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20690%20Villagers%20United%20to%20Save%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Animals%20from%20Extreme%20Thirst%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESummer%20is%20hard.%20And%20in%20dry%20regions%20where%20the%20sun%20is%20at%20its%20fiercest%2C%20even%20stepping%20out%20of%20the%20house%20becomes%20a%20daily%20struggle.%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20this%20difficult%20for%20us%20%E2%80%94%20with%20water%20bottles%2C%20fans%2C%20and%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20imagine%20what%20it%20must%20be%20like%20for%20stray%20animals%20and%20birds%2C%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F326836%2Fsai-vignesh-rescuer-activist-started-almighty-animal-care-trust-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesperate%20for%20just%20a%20little%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20water%20to%20get%20through%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20People%20for%20Animals%20(PfA)%2C%20in%20March%202024%20alone%2C%20over%2088.2%20per%20cent%20of%20birds%2C%20and%205.9%20percent%20of%20reptiles%20and%20mammals%20rescued%20were%20found%20to%20be%20dehydrated.%20If%20these%20numbers%20are%20alarming%20in%20a%20relatively%20greener%20city%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20with%20its%20harsher%2C%20drier%20climate%20%E2%80%94%20is%20even%20more%20dire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20seven%20friends%20from%20the%20village%20of%20Bawarla%20near%20Jodhpur%20decided%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20just%20stand%20by%20and%20watch.%20What%20began%20as%20a%20simple%20effort%20to%20place%20bowls%20of%20water%20and%20grain%20for%20animals%20has%20transformed%20into%20%E2%80%98Jeev%20Jantu%20Premee%20Bandhu%20Sanstha%E2%80%99%20(Friends%20Who%20Love%20Living%20Beings)%2C%20a%20grassroots%20movement%20with%20over%20690%20active%20members%20across%2035%20villages%2C%20all%20united%20by%20one%20mission%3A%20to%20ensure%20no%20living%20being%20dies%20of%20thirst%20or%20hunger%20during%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20punishing%20summers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeaths%20due%20to%20dehydration%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20regions%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20temperatures%20often%20soar%20above%2045%C2%B0C%2C%20dehydration%20can%20prove%20fatal%20for%20animals.%20This%20became%20painfully%20clear%20during%20the%20pandemic%20summer%20of%202021.%20The%20pandemic%20had%20gripped%20the%20country%2C%20but%20another%20silent%20tragedy%20was%20unfolding%20in%20the%20arid%20corners%20of%20Jodhpur%2C%20Rajasthan%3A%20animals%20and%20birds%20were%20collapsing%20from%20heat%20and%20thirst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20heard%20that%20even%20animals%20like%20camels%2C%20which%20can%20withstand%20drought%2C%20were%20dying%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20water%2C%20I%20knew%20this%20can%E2%80%99t%20continue%20for%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dinesh%20Bishnoi%2C%20an%20officer%20at%20AIIMS%20Jodhpur%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajasthan%20is%20a%20dry%20place%2C%20in%20many%20ways%20a%20man-made%20desert.%20There%20are%20barely%20any%20trees%20apart%20from%20Khejri%20and%20Kair.%20Animals%20have%20very%20limited%20access%20to%20food%2C%20shade%2C%20and%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prakash%20Bishnoi%2C%20a%20nurse%20superintendent%20with%20the%20railways%20and%20a%20core%20member%20of%20the%20Jeev%20Jantu%20Premee%20Bandhu%20Sanstha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3